description:
Matrix inversion via LU decomposition, linear system solving for `Ax = b`, batch solve for multiple right-hand sides.

## Operations

```rust
impl<F: FiniteField> FieldMatrix<F> {
    pub fn inv(&self) -> Option<FieldMatrix<F>>;
    pub fn solve(&self, b: &FieldVec<F>) -> Option<FieldVec<F>>;
    pub fn solve_batch(&self, b: &FieldMatrix<F>) -> Option<FieldMatrix<F>>;
    pub fn det(&self) -> F;
}
```

- `inv` — matrix inversion via LU, returns `None` for singular matrices
- `solve` — solve `Ax = b` for a single right-hand side
- `solve_batch` — solve `AX = B` for multiple right-hand sides simultaneously
- `det` — determinant via LU decomposition

## Dependencies

- Gaussian elimination and LU decomposition (c3f8c1cb)
